    "First, we describe the literature search methodology that was applied to recover the studies described herein.",
    "What follows is an abridged introduction to selfsupervised learning.",
    "We then present evidence for the merits of SSL as reported by a selection of recent studies -a separate section is dedicated to each of MRI, CT, X-ray, and US.",
